structure S where
  carrier : Type
  mul : carrier → carrier → carrier
def Nat.S : S where
  carrier := Nat
  mul := (· * ·)
def Int.S : S where
  carrier := Int
  mul := (· * ·)
unif_hint (s : S) where
  s =?= Nat.S ⊢ s.carrier =?= Nat
unif_hint (s : S) where
  s =?= Int.S ⊢ s.carrier =?= Int
def mul {s : S}
